Alaska 2023🎣 Part I
-
After years of my bro trying to convince me to visit him I finally caved last year. Instantly I fell in love with this beautiful state. I’m so grateful my family makes every year more special. I’m a Floridian to the core but a part of my heart will always be in Alaska💙❄️

If I wanted to hurt anyone here🔥😈

Alaska 2023🏔️🚁Part II
-
Riding a helicopter to the top of a glacier and drinking the natural water with my family is a core memory. People always ask if Alaska is cold… I go at the end of June and it’s ~70F⛅️
